branchCategory.name: JSY Non Plug-in
branchCategory.description: <p>Non plug-in type for JSY series is available in 3 valve body sizes, JSY1000 (6.4mm), JSY3000 (10mm) and JSY5000 (15mm).  It is available in side porting and bottom porting.  Non plug-in JSY is also available in dual 3-port configuration.</p>
